message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present you with our premium product, which I believe would greatly benefit your business. Given its exceptional value and quality, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $950000. This is a unique opportunity to acquire a product that is worth $800000 to you at a competitive rate. Should you have any questions or require further information, please do not hesitate to reach out. I look forward to the possibility of working with you.
